General.Name: Clinical Laserthermia Systems AB (publ)
General.Description: Clinical Laserthermia Systems AB (publ) develops treatment tools for diseased tissue under the TRANBERG brand in Sweden. The company offers TRANBERG, a thermal therapy system designed to deliver laser energy to heat the target tissue. It also provides mobile laser unit, a controlling component with a wavelength of 1064 nanometers provides multiple options to control treatment. In addition, the company offers various gauge laser applicators, as well as provides temperature and treatment monitoring devices. Clinical Laserthermia Systems AB (publ) was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
